 2001-19212001-10-230,  ,  ,  ,  HERITAGE
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of CAROL W. McDONALD, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the Canadian Museum of Nature to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Arthur W. May, whose term has expired.
